-- EasyJet Founder Stelios Won’t Support Pay Report, Telegraph Says
-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 2012-01-22T08:52:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-22/easyjet-founder-stelios-won-t-support-pay-report-telegraph-says.html
Stelios Haji Ioannou, the founder
and largest shareholder of  EasyJet Plc (EZJ) , won’t support its
executives’ pay report,  the Sunday Telegraph  reported.  Stelios, who goes by his first name, will vote against the
remuneration report at the low-cost airline’s annual general
meeting, he told the newspaper in an e-mail.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Ermakova in London at 
